  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink35-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">vāyilāyp pukuntār talaimakaṉ kuṇaṅ kūṟiyavaḻi ‘avaṉukku illātaṉavē
          kūṟutalāl, ippoḻutukāṇ eṉ mēṉi pacantatu’ eṉat talaimakaḷ tōḻikkuc colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink35">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> amma vāḻi tōḻi nammūrp</l>
          <l> poykai yāmpa ṉāruri meṉkā</l>
          <l> ṉiṟattiṉu niḻaṟṟutaṉ maṉṉē</l>
          <l> yiṉippacan taṉṟeṉ māmaik kaviṉē</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> Alas, [my] friend!</l>
          <l> There is for sure  a shining brighter than the colour</l>
          <l> of the soft stems stripped of bark(?) of the white lotus in the pond</l>
          <l> by our village.</l>
          <l> My dark beauty has now paled.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
